
For cd-hit

How to compile?
  1. Compile without multi-threading support: make
  2. Compile with multi-threading support: make openmp=yes



For cd-hit-auxtools
  cd cd-hit-auxtools
  make


For psi-cd-hit
  please download legacy BLAST (not BLAST+) and install the executables in your $PATH


For more information, please visith <a href="http://cd-hit.org">http://cd-hit.org</a> or please read the cd-hit-users-guide.pdf. 
